  <user-story>
    <as-a>user (viewer or maker)</as-a>
    <i-want>to receive push notifications for important marketplace events</i-want>
    <so-that>I stay informed about offers, bids, auctions, and order updates</so-that>
  </user-story>
  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion id="ac1">**SECURITY CRITICAL**: App requests push notification permission on first launch with clear value proposition, respecting user choice without aggressive re-prompting.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac2">Device token registration with Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) for both iOS and Android, with automatic token refresh handling and server synchronization.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac3">Device token stored securely on Serverpod with user association, platform identification, and token expiry tracking.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac4">**RELIABILITY CRITICAL**: Automatic token refresh and re-registration on app launch, token invalidation, or platform updates within 60 seconds.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac5">Multiple device support per user with independent token management and delivery tracking across devices.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac6">Background notification handling when app is closed or backgrounded with proper deep linking to relevant screens.</criterion>
    <criterion id="ac7">Foreground notification handling with custom in-app display and immediate activity feed updates.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
